        <mxCell id="c2" value="THE DOMAIN MODEL  (model-artifact — the narrow waist)&#xa;stable synthetic IDs (DD-004) · rich types · user facts first-class &amp; durable&#xa;computed graphs (call graph / CFG) · P-code escape hatch (DD-003) · semantic-zoom altitude (DD-020)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=13;fontFamily=Menlo;fillColor=#0d1526;strokeColor=#27d4ff;fontColor=#d6f2ff;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
